#: ../../../doc/en/example/markers.rst:311
msgid ""
"This is equivalent to directly applying the decorator to the two test "
"functions."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/example/markers.rst:314
msgid ""
"To apply marks at the module level, use the :globalvar:`pytestmark` global "
"variable::"
